# UI Design Guidelines

## Brand Identity
- Create a unique, consistent design style across all screens
- Use the app's brand colors consistently:
  - Primary teal: #44D7D0
  - Dark background: #0F1520 to #000000 gradient
  - Text on dark: white or light gray

## Visual Elements
- Implement frosted glass effect (glass_card_widget) for cards and containers
- Use subtle animations for transitions and interactions
- Maintain high contrast between text and backgrounds
- Use rounded corners (borderRadius) consistently across the app

## Typography
- Use system fonts (no custom fonts)
- Establish clear text hierarchy with consistent sizes:
  - Headings: Bold, larger size
  - Body text: Regular weight, medium size
  - Secondary text: Light weight, smaller size

## Layout
- Design for iPhone 15 Pro dimensions (393 x 852 pixels)
- Implement responsive layouts that work across different screen sizes
- Use consistent padding and spacing throughout the app
- Organize content with clear visual hierarchy

## Navigation
- Use bottom tab navigation with 4 main sections:
  - 创作 (Creation/Photo Editor)
  - 好事 (Good Things Journal)
  - 茶记 (Tea Tracker)
  - 我的 (Settings/Profile)
- Ensure smooth transitions between screens